Global Active Buzzer Market Insights
Active Buzzer Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Active Buzzer Market Overview
The active buzzer market is anticipated to witness steady growth due to the increasing demand for electronic components in various industries. As of 2024, the global market size for active buzzers is valued at approximately USD 1.4 billion. With advancements in technology, active buzzers are being used in automotive, healthcare, consumer electronics, and home appliances. Their ability to alert and signal through sound makes them indispensable in alarm systems, security, and notification devices. The market growth is also driven by the growing demand for smart home applications and IoT-enabled devices.

